{"tid":540138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錢大康昨午稱未直接收學生求助　陳樂行稱前日已求助質疑錢不關心","createTime":"2018-01-25T08:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T08:27:59.000Z","uid":33959,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea73ff6fd7f6f2cfc876dd40b3229c65a69ad410","tid":540138,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"參與抗議普通話豁免試行動的浸會大學學生陳樂行，接獲逾百則包含「 殺死你」、「解剖你」的恐嚇信息，他形容人身受威脅。浸大校長錢大康昨午見傳媒時稱，未直接收到學生求助，但陳樂行今早於商台節目表示，他當日已透過區議員向錢大康發電郵，而錢大康昨早已回覆了電郵，認為錢大康昨午對傳媒的說法「好奇怪」。<br />\n<br />\n陳樂行在電台節目上憶述，他前天（23日）於廣州醫院實習時，收到包含「殺死你」、「解剖你」的恐嚇電話及信息，令整間醫院感到不安。<br />\n<br />\n陳樂行稱，當日中午致電浸大校友、區議員楊雪盈求助，對方即時向校長錢大康發電郵講述事件，至昨日（24日）早上10時獲錢大康署名回覆，稱「會在有需要時提供協助」，故對錢大康昨日下午4時對傳媒說沒有直接收到學生求助感到「奇怪」，「為何（錢大康）可以一方面覆說收到求助，一方面對傳媒說沒收到同學求助？看不到校長對學生人身安全有什麼關心」。<br />\n<br />\n至於被點名是「港獨」分子，陳樂行強調自己不是「港獨」分子，從無發表過支持「港獨」的言論，亦無參與過「港獨」行動。他表示，希望校方陪同他報警及提供法律支援，但對至今仍未收到錢大康慰問感到遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180125/s00001/1516845492962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180125%2Fs00001%2F1516845492962&d=Q%2FfuHUrffkCmMTVCp%2FMfQ7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=e9e5ad6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180125%2Fs00001%2F1516845492962&h=71cb0984\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180125/s00001/1516845492962</a><br />\n<br />\n商台直播link：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10155670541163876&amp;id=8723358875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10155670541163876%26id%3D8723358875&d=Q%2FfuHUrffkCmMTVCp%2FMfQ7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=196b6a3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10155670541163876&amp;id=8723358875</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/160629_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F160629_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7f930269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/161149_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F161149_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2bc6ea4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a8c3644f6b11f03e66ada9ac0a40fe6f05c0ebd","tid":540138,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傻喇,而家只要你一反對就幫你打上 港獨 標籤"},{"pid":"2f7cdf159e661d927374c0b320606d9fac0eb8e4","tid":540138,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"港獨撚召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84da212c70591137909f96f062a8119832c19123","tid":540138,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:27:59.000Z","msg":"條奶共狗緊係視而不見啦<br />\n點會幫你啊 有哂共狗立場既校長"}]}